：自由选择的结局！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125490/extras/2bec6cb341fcaa1461eca58858f2d828.poster.avif?t=1729880855\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125490/extras/2bec6cb341fcaa1461eca58858f2d828.webm?t=1729880855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125490/extras/2bec6cb341fcaa1461eca58858f2d828.mp4?t=1729880855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>开启你奇妙的外星旅途吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125490/extras/b9f47c3c529135679d5dce94ca42cf6b.poster.avif?t=1729880855\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125490/extras/b9f47c3c529135679d5dce94ca42cf6b.webm?t=1729880855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125490/extras/b9f47c3c529135679d5dce94ca42cf6b.mp4?t=1729880855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>————————————————————————————</strong><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2></strong><br>1、自由打造外星探索团队：工程师、科学家、变种人战士、军队……<br>2、在外星从零开始建造基地。<br>3、数百种可招募的战棋对战棋子……<br>4、上千种各类外星生物。<br>5、丰富的外星文明种族：昆虫人，硅基生命，超级生命体等。<br>6、阵营对抗：美国、中国、欧洲等各国探索队为争夺资源开启纷争。",
